# Library Management System

A simple Spring Boot-based Library Management System that allows for managing books, users, borrowing/returning books, and more. This project also implements JWT-based authentication and Swagger UI for API documentation.

## Prerequisites
- Java 21
- Maven
- PostgreSQL
- IDE (IntelliJ IDEA)
- Postman (for testing APIs)

## Features
- User Registration and Authentication
- Book Management (CRUD operations)
- Book Borrowing and Returning
- Book Categories


